snippet.title: Aretha II [アレサ ２] Game Sample - SNES/SFC
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: September 18th, 2008

This is a sample video for the second Aretha (Aretha II: Ariel no Fushigi na Tabi, or アレサII アリエルの不思議な旅) game for the Super Famicom. This video was cut almost in half to get rid of any major spoilers since the game is directly related to the previous. This game added a little more of everything, although it got rid of the interesting "music merging" aspect.

You can read an article on it at:

http://www.gamingsanctuary.com/Aretha2_MR.html
